#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/shadow.md:11
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Armor Class** 12    \n"
"**Hit Points** 16 (3d8 + 3)    \n"
"**Speed** 40 ft. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/shadow.md:15
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"| STR     | DEX     | CON     | INT     | WIS     | CHA     |\n"
"|---------|---------|---------|---------|---------|---------|\n"
"| 6 (−2)  | 14 (+2) | 13 (+1) | 6 (−2)  | 10 (+0) | 8 (−1)  |\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/shadow.md:24
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Skills** Stealth +4 (+6 in dim light or darkness)    \n"
"**Damage Vulnerabilities.** radiant    \n"
"**Damage Resistances** acid, cold, fire, lightning, thunder; bludgeoning, "
"piercing, and slashing from nonmagical attacks    \n"
"**Damage Immunities** necrotic, poison    \n"
"**Condition Immunities** exhaustion, frightened, grappled, paralyzed, "
"petrified, poisoned, prone, restrained    \n"
"**Senses** darkvision 60 ft., passive Perception 10    \n"
"**Languages** --    \n"
"**Challenge** 1/2 (100 XP) \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/shadow.md:28
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Amorphous.** The shadow can move through a space as narrow as 1 inch wide "
"without squeezing.    \n"
"**Shadow Stealth.** While in dim light or darkness, the shadow can take the "
"Hide action as a bonus action.    \n"
"**Sunlight Weakness.** While in sunlight, the shadow has disadvantage on "
"attack rolls, ability checks, and saving throws. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/shadow.md:31
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"### Actions \n"
"**Strength Drain.** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one "
"creature. _Hit:_ 9 (2d6 + 2) necrotic damage, and the target's Strength "
"score is reduced by 1d4. The target dies if this reduces its Strength to "
"0. Otherwise, the reduction lasts until the target finishes a short or long "
"rest.    \n"
"If a non-evil humanoid dies from this attack, a new shadow rises from the "
"corpse 1d4 hours later.\n"
msgstr ""
